      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引岳士奎同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳士奎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，岳士奎。奉了圣上旨意，准备酒宴，与太君长亭饯行。\n来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳士奎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长亭去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
